.. [NEA] http://www.oecd-nea.org/dbdata/data/manual-endf/endf102_MT.pdf
.. [T2] http://t2.lanl.gov/endf/mts.html
.. [JAEA] http://wwwndc.jaea.go.jp/form/ENDF6/mt.html

